{"tid":927232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港生熱選地】留學澳洲遭性騷擾嚴重 華裔男啞忍身心重創","createTime":"2018-12-04T04:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T10:33:30.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f2ee1371f45203d983f669efa536d49c299ea54a","tid":927232,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:34:38.000Z","msg":"(內容新增)不少中港台學生都會選擇到澳洲留學，為當地年創逾240億澳元（逾1,372億港元）產值，令教育成為澳洲的第三大產業。當地教育部2018年最新報告顯示，在澳留學生人數已達64萬，其中53%來自亞洲國家，當中又以中國留學生最多。然而，近年當地針對留學生的性侵案卻不斷增加，澳洲人權委員會前年進行訪問，就發現來自39間大學、超過3萬名留學生中，每5名受訪者就有1名表示曾遭性騷擾。<br />\n一名來自馬來西亞的華裔男留學生Sonny，就讀墨爾本東部某知名大學。他是同性戀，到澳洲後參加了學生社交派對，未料翌日醒來卻驚覺肛裂出血，並伴隨劇烈疼痛，之後他才得悉自己遭人下藥性侵。由於Sonny對所經歷的性事並無清晰記憶，不記得自己是否曾同意或願意發生性行為，所以沒有選擇報警。但事件已對他心理造成嚴重創傷，甚至影響日常生活與學習。<br />\n在澳洲留的外國學生遭性侵的情況嚴重，而更令人擔憂的是，許多受害人因怕惹麻煩或恐被遣返而啞忍。曾有遭性侵的中國女留學生勇敢報警，卻只換來警方一句話：「這不是你的錯，下次小心。」而校方為免影響招生，大多都會竭盡所能掩飾事實。<br />\n到底在澳留學生遭性侵案持續增加的原因為何？哪些地方是發生慘劇的高危地點？受害人又該如何求助？欲知詳情，即睇動新聞！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181203/large/1543847397_571c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181203%2Flarge%2F1543847397_571c.jpg&h=c7bea521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181204/58985701\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181204%2F58985701&d=c2Oj08GKES16mIsH3YW0tjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=33f6cc39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181204%2F58985701&h=0791c1aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181204/58985701</a>"},{"pid":"e527946588b03c1459eebce567fc39974cb9f612","tid":927232,"uid":93479,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:06:23.000Z","msg":"正正經經讀書唔得嘅<br />\n<br />\n你又唔見 詹天佑，孫中山，徐志摩 等放洋留學會出事？"},{"pid":"fca21586e38b4308fac982b041a47a1f5d5ebcf9","tid":927232,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae931128aa71d6feedb302671f05c02ef04a210","tid":927232,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a79b0f59de51cb37c5c90552e2fb57e058cbe9b","tid":927232,"uid":172024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:30:50.000Z","msg":"有53% 黎自亞洲國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2930cde5a8752a9794e44bdb03af9a6ed5dd57a8","tid":927232,"uid":65774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a79b0f59de51cb37c5c90552e2fb57e058cbe9b","tid":927232,"uid":172024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:30:50.000Z","msg":"有53% 黎自亞洲國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:32:29.000Z","msg":"我仲以為起碼80%留學生係來自亞洲tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1518454989689353a7875f11c9f30b28c62a2cb","tid":927232,"uid":14566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a79b0f59de51cb37c5c90552e2fb57e058cbe9b","tid":927232,"uid":172024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:30:50.000Z","msg":"有53% 黎自亞洲國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:33:45.000Z","msg":"本身亞洲佔全球一半人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5710c6a3c50d546944a7520fcf8995e3928096d","tid":927232,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T09:38:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e01d7668890c34f5